### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### 1. Get Hello - Root endpoint
GET {{baseUrl}}/

### 2. Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### 3. Get All Users
GET {{baseUrl}}/users

### 4. Create User
POST {{baseUrl}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "role": "user"
}
